Pattern Recognition Layer

The system does not identify the person.
The system recognizes continuity of pattern.

Core fields:

device_signature
sensor_pattern
environment_pattern

Definitions:

device_signature = stable trace of the device and technical entry conditions
sensor_pattern = signal behavior pattern observed during measurement
environment_pattern = ambient pattern of the measurement environment

Purpose:

To detect repeated similarity without storing personal identity.

The system may internally recognize:

- same or similar device entry
- same or similar signal behavior
- same or similar environment conditions

This does not mean:
- identity
- name
- ownership

It means:
pattern continuity
